					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Well poopy! I liked my idea so much, too. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />
<br />
<br />Anyway, you will only get 8 consecutive IRQs if you <em>don't</em> decode the lower 4 bits of the PPU's fetch address. Remember, you'd be looking specifically for 0FE0 or 1FE0, which is only the <em>first row</em> of the first plane of tile FE in their respective pattern tables. That's only fetched once for each time tile FE gets rendered.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

