						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Drag wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Given this, sprite 0 will always cause an $FE IRQ on PPU cycle 260. No other sprite has any similar guarantee though, it's just sprite 0.</div>
<br />I imagine that if you always use the topmost sprites (from 0 up) for IRQs and those don't appear on the same scanlines, it should OK (i.e. if you use sprite 1 for a second IRQ after sprite 0 has been fully rendered, both would happen at the same point in the scanline).</div>

